Global Cyber Threat Intelligence Market Insights
Cyber Threat Intelligence Market size was valued at USD 10.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 29.24 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 15.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Cyber Threat Intelligence Market Overview
The global Cyber Threat Intelligence Market is valued at approximately USD 11.4 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 23.6%, reaching an estimated USD 45.3 billion by 2032. This growth is driven by the increasing need for organizations to defend against sophisticated cyber threats. Rising cyber-attacks, adoption of IoT devices, and the growing volume of sensitive data are fueling the demand for advanced cyber threat intelligence solutions. Enterprises across multiple sectors such as BFSI, healthcare, IT & telecom, and retail are integrating threat intelligence platforms to mitigate risks and enhance their security posture.

